xwikidoc.content: {{include document="XWiki.LiveTableResultsMacros"/}} {{velocity wiki="false"}} ## Macro to extend the default LiveTable row #macro(extendRow $row) #set($lastExecution=$NULL) ## Get the product version which was last tested. #set($statement = "select execution.product from Document as doc, doc.object(QA.ExecutionClass) as execution where execution.test = :test order by execution.date desc") #set($product = $services.query.xwql($statement).bindValue("test", "${row.doc_space}.${row.doc_name}").setLimit(1).execute()) #if(!$product.isEmpty()) #set($statement = "select execution.browser, execution.database, execution.servletContainer from Document as doc, doc.object(QA.ExecutionClass) as execution where execution.product = :product and execution.test = :test") #set($results = $services.query.xwql($statement).bindValue("product", $product.get(0)).bindValue("test", "${row.doc_space}.${row.doc_name}").execute()) ## RESULTS: $results.class.name ## PRODUCT: $product #set($productPage = $xwiki.getDocument($product.get(0))) #set($productObject = $productPage.getObject('QA.ProductClass')) ## $productObject.class.name #if(!$productObject) #set($discard = $row.put("product", "$product")) #else #set($discard = $row.put("product", "$productObject.getProperty('name').value $productObject.getProperty('version').value")) #end ## ## ## Build a map for each browser and database with their all tested versions ## $product #set($browsers = {}) #set($databases = {}) #set($servletContainers = {}) #foreach($result in $results) #set($browserValue=$result.get(0)) #set($databaseValue=$result.get(1)) #set($servletContainerValue=$result.get(2)) #set($browserDoc=$xwiki.getDocument($browserValue)) #set($databaseDoc=$xwiki.getDocument($databaseValue)) #set($servletContainerDoc=$xwiki.getDocument($servletContainerValue)) #if($browserDoc.getObject('QA.BrowserClass')) #set($browserName = $browserDoc.get('name')) #set($browserVersions = $browsers.get($browserName)) #if(!$browserVersions) #set($browserVersions = $collectionstool.getSet()) #set($discard = $browsers.put($browserName, $browserVersions)) #end #set($discard = $browserVersions.add($browserDoc.get('version'))) #else #set($discard = $browsers.put($browserValue, '')) #end #if($databaseDoc.getObject('QA.DatabaseClass')) #set($databaseName = $databaseDoc.get('name')) #set($databaseVersions = $databases.get($databaseName)) #if(!$databaseVersions) #set($databaseVersions = $collectionstool.getSet()) #set($discard = $databases.put($databaseName, $databaseVersions)) #end #set($discard = $databaseVersions.add($databaseDoc.get('version'))) #else #set($discard = $databases.put($databaseValue, '')) #end #if($servletContainerDoc.getObject('QA.ServletContainerClass')) #set($servletContainerName = $servletContainerDoc.get('name')) #set($servletContainerVersions = $servletContainers.get($servletContainerName)) #if(!$servletContainerVersions) #set($servletContainerVersions = $collectionstool.getSet()) #set($discard = $servletContainers.put($servletContainerName, $servletContainerVersions)) #end #set($discard = $servletContainerVersions.add($servletContainerDoc.get('version'))) #else #set($discard = $servletContainers.put($servletContainerValue, '')) #end #end ## We get an image for each browser and put the versions #set($browsersHTML='') #foreach($browser in $sorttool.sort($browsers.entrySet(), 'key:asc')) #set($browserIcon = $browser.key+'.png') ## Sort (String sort, not Integer sort) #set($browser.value = $sorttool.sort($browser.value)) #set($browsersHTML = $browsersHTML + "" + "$browser.value.toString().replace('[', '').replace(']', '') " + "") #end ## Browsers: $browsers ## HTML: $browsersHTML #set($discard = $row.put("browsers","$browsersHTML")) ## We get an image for each database and put the versions #set($databasesHTML='') #foreach($database in $sorttool.sort($databases.entrySet(), 'key:asc')) #set($databaseIcon = $database.key+'.png') ## Sort (String sort, not Integer sort) #set($database.value = $sorttool.sort($database.value)) #if ("$!database.value" == '') #set ($databaseValue = '') #else #set ($databaseValue = $database.value.toString().replace('[', '').replace(']', '')) #end #set($databasesHTML = $databasesHTML + "" + "$databaseValue " + "") #end #set($discard = $row.put("databases","$databasesHTML")) ## We get an image for each servlet container and put the versions #set($servletContainersHTML='') #foreach($servletContainer in $sorttool.sort($servletContainers.entrySet(), 'key:asc')) #set($servletContainerIcon = $servletContainer.key+'.png') ## Sort (String sort, not Integer sort) #set($servletContainer.value = $sorttool.sort($servletContainer.value)) #set($servletContainersHTML = $servletContainersHTML + "" + "$!{servletContainer.value.toString().replace('[', '').replace(']', '')} " + "") #end #set($discard = $row.put("servletContainers","$servletContainersHTML")) #else #set($discard = $row.put("product", $services.localization.render('qaapp.WebHome.LiveTable.no.tests.execution.found'))) #set($discard = $row.put("browsers", '')) #set($discard = $row.put("databases", '')) #set($discard = $row.put("servletContainers", '')) #end #set($test = "${row.doc_space}.${row.doc_name}") #set($discard = $row.put("doc_runTest_url", $xwiki.getURL($row.doc_fullName, 'get', "sheet=QA.ExecutionAddSheet"))) ##ExtendRow Macro End #end #**# #if($xcontext.action == 'get' && "$!{request.outputSyntax}" == 'plain') $response.setContentType('application/json') #set($map = {}) #set($filterWhere = '') #set($filterParams = []) #if("$!request.testSpace" != '' || $request.testSpace == '') #set($filterWhere = "and doc.space = ?") #set($discard = $filterParams.add($request.testSpace)) #end ## ## #gridresultwithfilter_buildJSON('QA.TestClass' ['doc.title', 'doc.space', 'automated','deprecated', 'userType', 'wikiType'] '' $filterWhere $filterParams $map) #foreach ($row in $map.rows) #extendRow($row) #end $jsontool.serialize($map) #else Custom LiveTableResults page used for computing the results for the LiveTables used from QA.WebHome and from the WebHome of the Test Spaces #end {{/velocity}}
